Fix this by testing the value of 'TCQ_F_CPUSTATS' bit in 'qdisc->flags',
before dereferencing 'qdisc->cpu_qstats'.

Fixes: 8a53e616de29 ("net: sched: when clearing NOLOCK, clear TCQ_F_CPUSTATS, too")
